-- Southern All Stars' Kuwata Has Cancer, Will Postpone Release of New Album
-- Go Onomitsu
-- 2010-07-28T04:18:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/southern-all-stars-kuwata-has-cancer-will-postpone-release-of-new-album.html

          
          
             Amuse Inc. said singer Keisuke
Kuwata of the Southern All Stars is suffering early-stages of
cancer of the esophagus and will postpone the release of a new
album that had been scheduled for Oct. 20. He will also cancel a
tour scheduled for Oct. 21 to Dec. 31, the company said in a
release to the Tokyo Stock Exchange.  
